Package: lcmc
Architecture: all
Depends: oracle-java8-jre | openjdk-8-jre,
 java-wrappers, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux Cluster Management Console
 The LCMC is a GUI application that configures, manages and visualizes high-
 availability clusters. Specifically it manages clusters that use one or more
 of these components: Pacemaker, Corosync, Heartbeat, DRBD, KVM, XEN and LVM.
